Write a 5-section report of approximately 600-700 words:
1. Opening — what the assessment revealed about ${n} specifically, referencing 3-4 of the most diagnostic observations by name
2. "What this profile means" — what it implies for how ${n} currently learns and why standard drilling may or may not work for them in 11+ preparation
